        public double get_sum_of_clauses_if_i_stay_as_i_am()
        Goes through every soft clause in which the actual literal occurs. And sums up the weight if the current clause is sattisfied.
        Returns:
        Sum of weight (no exp modification, just the sum)

      • get_sum_of_clauses_if_i_am_swapped

        public double get_sum_of_clauses_if_i_am_swapped()
        Swaps the current literal. Goes through every soft clause in which the actual literal occurs. And sums up the weight if the current clause is sattisfied. Finally, it swaps the literal back.
